A. Holotype (LAMNH-AHF-2509), lateral view. B. Same, anterior end, lateral view showing abundant chaetae and long papillae. C. Non-type specimen, anterior end, frontal view, palps and branchiae removed (BS: branchial scars, LL: lateral lip, PS: palp scar, VV: ventral lip). D. Holotype, notochaetae from an anterior chaetiger. E. Same, neurochaetae from a median chaetiger, insert showing the tips. F. Same, neurochaetae from a posterior chaetiger, insert showing the tip. Scale bars: A: 5 mm, B: 1.5 mm, C: 0.5 mm, D: 150 µm, E: 60 µm, F: 50 µm.
</paragraph>
